PKT_EXCHANGE:

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   0 ! PktType       ! EX_Flags      ! 12 Byte AEAD_IV ...           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
     : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
     : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   0 : ...              ... AEAD_IV  ! destination MAC ...           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   4 : ... destination MAC ...                                       !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   8 ! source MAC ...                                                :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  12 : ... source MAC ...            ! source timeout                !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  16 ! source socket 1 ...                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  20 : ... source socket 1                                           !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  24 ! source socket 2 ...                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  28 : ... source socket 2                                           !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   Y : 16 Byte AEAD_ICV ...
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+4 : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+8 : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+12: ...                                             ... AEAD_ICV  :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

